12. Can you use Offline Power Apps?

EXPLAIN IN ANSWER:-
â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”
ğŸ‘‰ Yes, Power Apps Supports can be usd offline apps. Using the SaveData() and LoadData() Functions:

ğŸ”¹ SaveData(): Allows me to save data locally on the user's device, which can be accessed even when the app is offline.
ğŸ”¹ LoadData(): It is used to load that local data when the app is back online.

ğŸ‘‰ Once the app is back online, we can implement logic to sync data with the server using funtions like Patch(), Collect(),
    to update the data source with any changes made offline.
