â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”
ğŸ‘‰ Power Apps Security roles define what actions user can take on data, (eg: Read, Write, Delete) and controls access to apps, forms and records.
ğŸ‘‰ Security Roles are Managed in Mircosoft Dataverse and we can customized for each user or group.
ğŸ‘‰ We can assign predefined security roles like (System Adminstrator, Environment Maker) or we can create custom roles based on business needs.

âœ… For Example â€“ Employee Management App:
ğŸ”¹ Admin       â†’ Full access: all records + Settings screen.
ğŸ”¹ Manager     â†’ Limited access: team-specific reports.
ğŸ”¹ Employee    â†’ Can only view/edit their own profile.
