18. Solutions in Power Apps?

EXPLAIN IN ANSWER:-
â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”â”
ğŸ‘‰ Solutions group related componentsâ€”like apps, flows, tables, and security rolesâ€”into a single package.
ğŸ‘‰ This simplifies managing, transporting, and deploying across different environments (Dev, Test, Prod).
ğŸ‘‰ In development, unmanaged solutions allow edits and ongoing changes.
ğŸ‘‰ For production, I export managed solutionsâ€”read-only, ensuring stability and controlled updates.

âœ… Benefits:
1. Streamlines version control and dependency management.
2. Enables smooth ALM (Application Lifecycle Management).
3. Supports team collaboration and easier maintenance.
